longBusinessSummary: Belrise Industries Limited manufactures and supplies automotive parts and components for two-wheeler, three-wheeler and four-wheeler passenger and commercial vehicle in India. It provides metal processing, polymer processing, surface treatment, mirror systems, suspension systems, foundry, home appliances, security hardware, e-mobility and floriculture components. Its products include chassis and BIW parts, exhaust systems, press and seating parts, cross-car beams, two-wheeler fairings, seat and side covers, two-wheeler fairings, luggage boxes, helmets, and headlight housings. The company also provides home security devices, such as locks and bolts; refrigerator vegetable trays, freezer grills, fridge baskets, and thermostat parts; outer and inner rearview mirrors for passenger and commercial vehicles; automotive systems, which include clutch and pressure plates, flywheel, control arm, crankshafts, housings, hub, and caliper products; and suspensions systems. Belrise Industries Limited was formerly known as Badve Engineering Limited and changed its name to Belrise Industries Limited in August 2022. The company was founded in 1988 and is based in Pune, India.
